---
title: Italian Pork Sausage & Kale Fried Rice with Grape Tomatoes, Chili Flakes & Scallions
description: Cozy up with this irresistible and inventive Italian-style fried rice that hits the table in a speedy 30 minutes! Savory Italian pork sausage, fresh grape tomatoes, garlic, and kale come together for a colorful, flavor-packed dish that's as delicious as it is easy to make.
